    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I was definitely in the mood for some chocolate cookies, and your recipe intrigued me. I had to use light raspberry yogurt instead of the plain, and I decided to add an egg because, well, it seemed like the right thing to do. The raspberry flavor was undetectable, and the egg made the cookies more cakelike and less chewy, but still delicious. The recipe was also a snap to make! Thank you for the inspiration!</p>
